Abstract = {This qualitative research aimed at understanding the experience of
   familiar caregivers in the process of caring for persons disabled by
   stroke, in their home. It was held in the Program of Domiciliary
   Assistance of a tertiary public hospital in Fortaleza-CE, with nine
   caregivers. The statements were obtained through interviews recorded and
